{
  "stem": "2522.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then they went back to the store until about 8 or 9 o'clock at night.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Trencin, because of the substantial Jewish community, there was a Jewish school.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You would call it, by American standards, a Jewish parochial school.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The school was adjoining the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were three classrooms.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And the first classroom was for the first two grades.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The second classroom was for the third grade.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the third classroom was for the fourth, fifth, and sixth grade.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the children pretty well knew one another from the synagogue and the classroom.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there was a very intense communication among these children, which continues to this day.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By and large, as a child, all of my social contact, particularly when I was in Jewish parochial grade school, was with other Jewish children, although, from time to time when my father took me visiting to the villages where his men were having their stores and their distribution, I visited with them and with their children.",
      "word_count": 57
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Also, we had employees in our store who were Gentile.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I got to know them pretty well, including some of my father's chief assistants.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I always had a great deal of exposure to, to people outside of the Jewish community.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But on an intense personal level, it was largely an introspective Jewish experience, particularly during my early youth.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, surely, because we were quite active as children.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] flowing through Trencin is a river where we used to go to swim.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, you know, once in a while, some other children threw stones at us and shouted Jew, Jew!",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we, we, we considered this, you know, as natural as mosquitoes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, and it was not very great apprehension.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
